'''登格赛里灯塔'''（{{lang-en| ''' Tangasseri Lighthouse'''}} 或 '''Thangassery Lighthouse'''）位于[[印度|印度]][[喀拉拉邦|喀拉拉邦]][[果拉姆县|奎隆县]][[奎隆|奎隆市]]下辖的{{tsl|en|Tangasseri|登格塞里}}小镇。它是{{tsl|en|Kollam metropolitan area|奎隆大都会区}}中仅有的两座灯塔之一（另一座是距其14公里的{{tsl|en|Kovilthottam Lighthouse|柯维滕泰灯塔}}），由'''-{zh-cn:戈奇;zh-tw:科契}-灯塔与{{tsl|en|Lightvessel|灯台船}}总局'''（{{lang-en|the Cochin Directorate General of Lighthouses and Lightships}}）维护管养<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dgll.nic.in/DLLChennai/530_1_DLLChennai.aspx |title=Chennai Directorate – Directorate General of Lighthouses and Lightships |publisher=Directorate General of Lighthouses and Lightships |accessdate=2015-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315010548/http://dgll.nic.in/DLLChennai/530_1_DLLChennai.aspx |archive-date=2015-03-15 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-national/tp-kerala/rs-111cr-project-to-beautify-road-to-tangasseri-lighthouse/article6562795.ece |title=Rs. 1.11-cr. project to beautify road to Tangasseri lighthouse |newspaper=[[印度报|印度报]] |accessdate=2015-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129074718/https://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-national/tp-kerala/rs-111cr-project-to-beautify-road-to-tangasseri-lighthouse/article6562795.ece |archive-date=2020-11-29}}</ref>。1902年的重建工程基本奠定了灯塔圆柱状塔身及红白斜条纹漆装的形态<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/kerala/tangasseri-lighthouse-to-stay-open-for-longer-hours/article5525671.ece |title=Tangasseri lighthouse to stay open for longer hours |newspaper=[[印度报|印度报]] |accessdate=2015-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429012946/http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/kerala/tangasseri-lighthouse-to-stay-open-for-longer-hours/article5525671.ece |archive-date=2014-04-29 }}</ref>，并使其初具41米的高度，在[[喀拉拉邦|喀拉拉邦]]海滨诸灯塔中仅次于位于-{zh-cn:[[科契|戈奇]];zh-tw:[[科契|科契]]}-的{{tsl|en|Vypin Lighthouse|维平灯塔}}（46米）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/kerala/new-look-for-tangasseri-lighthouse/article8634902.ece |title=New look for Tangasseri lighthouse |newspaper=[[印度报|印度报]] |accessdate=2016-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160523004657/http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/kerala/new-look-for-tangasseri-lighthouse/article8634902.ece |archive-date=2016-05-23 }}</ref> 。登格塞里灯塔也是当地的一个热门旅游目的地<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-national/tp-kerala/Lighthouse-sees-rise-in-footfall/article16952809.ece |title=Lighthouse sees rise in footfall |newspaper=[[印度报|印度报]] |accessdate=2016-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129061807/https://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-national/tp-kerala/Lighthouse-sees-rise-in-footfall/article16952809.ece |archive-date=2020-11-29}}</ref>。

== 历史 ==
灯塔所处的{{tsl|en|Tangasseri|登格塞里}}地区是欧洲人在[[印度次大陆|南亚次大陆]]最早的登陆地之一，1502年，[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]人首先在登格塞里建立了活动基地与贸易中转站，该地迅速成为了重要的[[香料贸易|香料贸易]]枢纽，并在1517年修建了防御工事{{tsl|en|St Thomas Fort|圣托马斯堡垒}}。随着[[荷兰东印度公司|荷兰东印度公司]]（VOC）的扩张，葡萄牙人和荷兰人在此地展开了长久的争夺，而圣托马斯堡垒也毁于其中，1661年荷兰人控制了登格塞里，之后的18世纪里，又有[[不列颠东印度公司|不列颠东印度公司]]（EIC）的殖民者与[[特拉凡哥尔|特拉凡哥尔王国]]参与对该地的争夺，直到1795年被英国人完全控制<ref>{{cite web |url=https://travel.manoramaonline.com/travel/essential-kerala/2018/03/27/thangasseri-kollam-port-lighthouse-sights-history.html |title=Thangassery: A flashback to Kerala's Portuguese past |publisher=On Manorama |accessdate=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129072349/https://www.onmanorama.com/travel/essential-kerala/2018/03/27/thangasseri-kollam-port-lighthouse-sights-history.html |archive-date=2020-11-29 }}</ref>。灯塔最初落成之前，EIC方面先搭建了一个简易的油灯塔楼供过往公司船只照明，同其它遍布海岸的类似设施连成一道光路，以确保夜间沿近海绕过[[科摩林角|科摩林角]]往来于[[阿拉伯海|阿拉伯海]]与[[孟加拉湾|孟加拉湾]]的航路畅通，部分位置关键的设施，包括登格塞里的灯塔在内得以保留与增筑，加上一些新建的灯塔，便形成了今日{{link-en|喀拉拉邦的灯塔分布|Category:Lighthouses_in_Kerala}}。1902年，灯塔增筑。1930年，灯塔产生开裂问题，以致需要泥瓦修补工作来确保灯塔的正常运作<ref name="Dgll">{{cite web |title=Indian Lighthouses: An Overview |url=http://www.dgll.nic.in/WriteReadData/Publication/Publication_Pdf_File/LighthousesofIndia(2).pdf |publisher=DGLL |accessdate=2014-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218163515/http://www.dgll.nic.in/WriteReadData/Publication/Publication_Pdf_File/LighthousesofIndia(2).pdf |archive-date=2014-12-18 }}</ref>。灯具进行过5次更换，分别是在1932年、1940年、1962年、1967年、1990年和1994年。 <ref name="Dgll"/>

2016年，灯塔新设了一部直通平台的观景电梯。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/kerala/Tangi%E2%80%99s-grand-old-lady-to-get-a-lift/article14593076.ece |title=Tangi's grand old lady to get a lift |newspaper=The Hindu |date=2016-08-27 |accessdate=2018-01-02 |archive-date=2021-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211003140655/https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/kerala/Tangi%E2%80%99s-grand-old-lady-to-get-a-lift/article14593076.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 位置 ==
灯塔坐落于登格塞里海滨岬角，登格塞里当地因历史与地理原因保留了完好的{{tsl|en|Anglo-Indian|盎格鲁-印地文化}}，许多殖民时期建筑也得以留存，如{{tsl|en|St_Thomas_Fort|托马斯堡废墟}}、{{tsl|en|Portuguese Cemetery, Kollam|葡萄牙人公墓}}、{{tsl|en|Buckingham Canal, Kollam|伯金汉运河}}、古{{tsl|en|Kollam Port|奎隆港}}，以及{{tsl|en|Infant Jesus Cathedral|圣婴座堂}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://rotarytangasseri.org/history.html |title=A brief history of Tangasseri |publisher=Rotary Club of Tangasseri |accessdate=2014-01-09  |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131122170529/http://rotarytangasseri.org/history.html |archivedate=2013-11-22 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.superbindiatours.com/Kerala/kollam.html |title=Superb India Tours – Kollam |publisher=Superb India Tours |accessdate=2014-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140129222013/http://www.superbindiatours.com/Kerala/kollam.html |archive-date=2014-01-29 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.oocities.org/athens/Acropolis/9669/tangy.htm |title=Tangasseri – OOCITIES |publisher=OOCITIES |accessdate=2014-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109123824/http://www.oocities.org/athens/Acropolis/9669/tangy.htm |archive-date=2015-01-09 }}</ref>。

灯塔对外开放的时间是[[印度标准时间|当地时间（UTC+05:30）]]除周一外每日的11:00-17:00<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.justkerala.in/increase-in-tangasseri-lighthouse-visiting-hours.php |title=Increase in Tangasseri Lighthouse Visiting Hours |publisher=Kerala News |accessdate=2015-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150331083524/http://news.justkerala.in/increase-in-tangasseri-lighthouse-visiting-hours.php |archive-date=2015-03-31 }}</ref>。

